title: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
subtitle: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposit directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (March 16 - April 12) will also receive:

- The new Ocelot Virtue
- 40% off Imani Tech Upgrades
- The Agency Vehicle Workshop
- The Pink Floral Tech Demon mask
- 75% off all Armor Plating, Ram Weapons, and Mines for the Brickade 6x6
- And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
